[
  {
    "segmentId": "01-opening-1",
    "chapterId": "01-opening",
    "step": 0,
    "path": "audio/01-opening/1.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 11220000,
    "text": "2026年7月1号，一个身家120多亿美元的科技CEO，坐在CNBC直播镜头前。...",
    "localPath": "audio/01-opening/1.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:4c8536b43ba497d0"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "01-opening-2",
    "chapterId": "01-opening",
    "step": 1,
    "path": "audio/01-opening/2.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 6435918,
    "text": "开场第一句话: Something has gone completely wrong. 有些东西已经彻底跑偏了。",
    "localPath": "audio/01-opening/2.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:5326224f5e780965"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "01-opening-3",
    "chapterId": "01-opening",
    "step": 2,
    "path": "audio/01-opening/3.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 6132925,
    "text": "他说企业花几百万买token，拿到零价值，自己的IP还被偷走。",
    "localPath": "audio/01-opening/3.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:9bd0632470b4ab95"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "01-opening-4",
    "chapterId": "01-opening",
    "step": 3,
    "path": "audio/01-opening/4.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 16913787,
    "text": "主持人Becky Quick愣了两秒: 你听起来很愤怒。他回了四个字: 这是报道。另一个主持人Sorkin插了一句: Sounds like shade. 这听...",
    "localPath": "audio/01-opening/4.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:484b16a546d438b9"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "01-opening-5",
    "chapterId": "01-opening",
    "step": 4,
    "path": "audio/01-opening/5.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 4375601,
    "text": "这个人是Palantir的CEO，Alex Karp。",
    "localPath": "audio/01-opening/5.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:16b9e05cb33549cc"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "01-opening-6",
    "chapterId": "01-opening",
    "step": 5,
    "path": "audio/01-opening/6.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 17250340,
    "text": "在接下来20分钟的直播里，他说了很多CEO不会在电视上说的大实话。而这些话，跟你每次打开ChatGPT、Claude、任何AI工具的那一刻，有直接的关系。",
    "localPath": "audio/01-opening/6.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:bd9f8a284735a9fd"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-1",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 0,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/1.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 6551882,
    "text": "我们先认真听一下，他到底说了什么。不只是金句，而是他的核心论证。",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/1.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:1395cf3d45a6d0e1"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-2",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 1,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/2.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 16525533,
    "text": "Karp的原话: I am going to chillax and waste my time with tokens, I am gonna get no ...",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/2.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:35ace2a67d63d191"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-3",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 2,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/3.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 5386984,
    "text": "不只是在说贵。他是在指出这个计费模型的方向性错误。",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/3.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:290396de91efc05e"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-4",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 3,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/4.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 9267619,
    "text": "他说，如果AI真能帮企业一天赚一亿美元，服务商为什么只按token收费，而不是分30%？",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/4.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:4ed35eb748e09cba"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-5",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 4,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/5.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 12762857,
    "text": "因为按token收费，本身就证明了这个产品无法定位价值。真正创造价值的东西，是按价值定价的。按用量收费，等于价值说不清。",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/5.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:2cbd4aa7b40e1f34"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-6",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 5,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/6.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 18185760,
    "text": "Karp说了一句很重的话: 当前的AI服务模式，是一种从亿万富翁开始、最终覆盖所有用户的不公平的财富税。企业支付token，换不来实际价值。自身的模型权重和核心...",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/6.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:258b5ac923a4a6bc"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-7",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 6,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/7.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 12997460,
    "text": "你注意这个词: 财富税。不是服务费。不是订阅费。是税。税的意思是什么？你必须交、无法讨价还价、而且你无法控制钱被怎么用。",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/7.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:d2a86d315e4b588b"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-8",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 7,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/8.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 19879456,
    "text": "客户的核心诉求其实特别简单: They want to know they own the means of production. 他们想确认自己拥有生产资料...",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/8.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:259a87f43c0a6d3b"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-9",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 8,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/9.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 14306349,
    "text": "他说客户要求在三个问题上有完全的自主权: 谁控制模型？谁掌控参数权重？谁掌握对应的企业价值？这三个问题，缺一个都不能算拥有。",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/9.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:f75546a01b74dd4c"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-10",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 9,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/10.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 17732971,
    "text": "Karp提出的行业底线: 谁拥有我的数据？数据存在哪？我的提示是否安全？信息是否传输给第三方？注意，他不是在问AI公司。他是在问你: 你用AI的时候，能回答这四...",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/10.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:3de58b4b0fddad41"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-11",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 10,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/11.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 19337914,
    "text": "好。四个论点，串起来看。Token模式的方向性错误，导致企业在交一笔财富税。这笔税的真正代价不是钱，是生产资料被转移。而要重建信任，每个人需要能回答四个最基本的...",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/11.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:1494d63d72abc63e"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "02-karp-arguments-12",
    "chapterId": "02-karp-arguments",
    "step": 11,
    "path": "audio/02-karp-arguments/12.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 6042993,
    "text": "你是不是已经隐约感觉到: 这套逻辑，好像不只是对企业成立？",
    "localPath": "audio/02-karp-arguments/12.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:70e7d2839f970949"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "03-enterprise-to-individual-1",
    "chapterId": "03-enterprise-to-individual",
    "step": 0,
    "path": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/1.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 21180454,
    "text": "我们来做一件事。把Karp的四个论点，一个字一个字地，从企业换成你。第一个。Token模式偷走价值。你每次打开AI对话框，是不是在用一种按用量付费的模式？月费、...",
    "localPath": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/1.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:80c2599a0f654f74"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "03-enterprise-to-individual-2",
    "chapterId": "03-enterprise-to-individual",
    "step": 1,
    "path": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/2.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 25383673,
    "text": "但按Karp的逻辑: 按用量收费本身就说明产品无法定位价值。那你问自己一个问题: 每次AI帮你写完一段文案、写完一段代码、回答完一个问题之后，你手里多了什么？多...",
    "localPath": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/2.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:a5e714d0d981b811"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "03-enterprise-to-individual-3",
    "chapterId": "03-enterprise-to-individual",
    "step": 2,
    "path": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/3.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 19497823,
    "text": "第二个。你在交财富税。你付费。你交出你的需求、你的思考逻辑、你的判断偏好。AI吸收了这些，变得更聪明、更懂你这类人。然后下一个人用同样的AI，得到了基于你贡献的...",
    "localPath": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/3.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:fb4e1a2f2d1b0b46"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "03-enterprise-to-individual-4",
    "chapterId": "03-enterprise-to-individual",
    "step": 3,
    "path": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/4.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 13206757,
    "text": "你交了钱。还交了数据。你得到了一次服务。AI公司得到了训练数据、长期订阅收入、用户行为图谱。谁的财富在增值？谁在交税？",
    "localPath": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/4.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:135bef67eb345678"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "03-enterprise-to-individual-5",
    "chapterId": "03-enterprise-to-individual",
    "step": 4,
    "path": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/5.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 27706077,
    "text": "第三个。你的生产资料正在被转移。Karp说企业想确认: 谁控制模型？谁掌控权重？谁掌握企业价值？翻译成你: 谁控制你的prompt库？谁掌握你的创作模板？那些只...",
    "localPath": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/5.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:8a700f20efdd07c0"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "03-enterprise-to-individual-6",
    "chapterId": "03-enterprise-to-individual",
    "step": 5,
    "path": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/6.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 15191746,
    "text": "你的生产资料不是GPU。是你的问题拆解方式，是你的审美判断，是你反复验证过的prompt模板，是你对好内容的定义。这些东西，现在在哪里？",
    "localPath": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/6.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:8d8f5c9b390b1fa5"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "03-enterprise-to-individual-7",
    "chapterId": "03-enterprise-to-individual",
    "step": 6,
    "path": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/7.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 18162676,
    "text": "第四个。你能回答那四个问题吗？你用ChatGPT写的东西，数据归谁？OpenAI的服务器上存了什么？你的prompt被拿去训练下一个模型了吗？你输出的内容，会不...",
    "localPath": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/7.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:87fcee533434821f"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "03-enterprise-to-individual-8",
    "chapterId": "03-enterprise-to-individual",
    "step": 7,
    "path": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/8.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 10466576,
    "text": "你发现没有，你答不上来。我不是说你应该答得上来。我说的是: 答不上来这件事本身，就是问题的答案。",
    "localPath": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/8.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:7aa2e513e843aaa2"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "03-enterprise-to-individual-9",
    "chapterId": "03-enterprise-to-individual",
    "step": 8,
    "path": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/9.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 27026667,
    "text": "这四个问题，从企业到个人，底层逻辑完全一样。只不过Karp的客户是CEO，你的客户是你自己。公司需要可控的生产资料才能竞争。你需要可控的能力资产才能不被替换。这...",
    "localPath": "audio/03-enterprise-to-individual/9.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:69cdf6b1ec062172"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "04-root-cause-1",
    "chapterId": "04-root-cause",
    "step": 0,
    "path": "audio/04-root-cause/1.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 26765261,
    "text": "但是，这里有个更深的问题要讲。Karp批判的是商业模式。但商业模式只是表象。底层的底层是: 大模型的工作原理，决定了它天然具有侵犯性。大模型最基础的工作方式是什...",
    "localPath": "audio/04-root-cause/1.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:93973f38c69c7102"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "04-root-cause-2",
    "chapterId": "04-root-cause",
    "step": 1,
    "path": "audio/04-root-cause/2.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 12038186,
    "text": "这意味着: 它对知识、技能的原创，天然具有吸收和再分配的本能。不是哪个公司坏。是这整件事的运作方式，就是这样。",
    "localPath": "audio/04-root-cause/2.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:e2cf82fa61ff6965"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "04-root-cause-3",
    "chapterId": "04-root-cause",
    "step": 2,
    "path": "audio/04-root-cause/3.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 18347619,
    "text": "我管这个叫写轮眼状态。看过火影的知道: 写轮眼可以复制对手的任何招式。在AI推动的大加速时代，模仿抄袭被加速到了这种程度: 原创者可能都无法识别对方是不是跟自己...",
    "localPath": "audio/04-root-cause/3.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:621cefcb3bac4108"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "04-root-cause-4",
    "chapterId": "04-root-cause",
    "step": 3,
    "path": "audio/04-root-cause/4.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 5121224,
    "text": "甚至可能反过来: 让人觉得是原创者在抄抄袭者。",
    "localPath": "audio/04-root-cause/4.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:c21f853b1be1b841"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "04-root-cause-5",
    "chapterId": "04-root-cause",
    "step": 4,
    "path": "audio/04-root-cause/5.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 21052789,
    "text": "我自己做自媒体之后，最焦虑的就是这个问题。我写的文章，记录灵光一现的感受和思想。但不远的将来，模型可以高速采集网上所有内容，复刻、洗稿、复杂重组。生成的东西，可...",
    "localPath": "audio/04-root-cause/5.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:a8c0aae268b895c1"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "04-root-cause-6",
    "chapterId": "04-root-cause",
    "step": 5,
    "path": "audio/04-root-cause/6.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 23717823,
    "text": "这对原创动力是根本性的打击。你的创造力产出的价值，在内容洪流里被稀释了。公司同理。原创的商业模式和产品，竞争对手可以近乎实时地学习复制。无法产生差异，就只能陷入...",
    "localPath": "audio/04-root-cause/6.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:689fd853d39bfe96"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "04-root-cause-7",
    "chapterId": "04-root-cause",
    "step": 6,
    "path": "audio/04-root-cause/7.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 17324263,
    "text": "所以你看: Karp指出来的Token模式方向性错误，是症状。大模型天然侵犯性，是病因。而你的生产资料不在你手里，是诊断结论。不管你是公司还是一个人，诊断结论是...",
    "localPath": "audio/04-root-cause/7.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:55fbf7b840cf9471"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "05-global-sovereignty-1",
    "chapterId": "05-global-sovereignty",
    "step": 0,
    "path": "audio/05-global-sovereignty/1.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 35036825,
    "text": "再拉远一点。生产资料归谁这个问题，不只在商业层面，它正在全球尺度上同时发生。Karp在美国喊不要依赖别人的API，要拥有自己的生产资料的同一个时期，中国对面向公...",
    "localPath": "audio/05-global-sovereignty/1.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:189048d845ae57a3"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "05-global-sovereignty-2",
    "chapterId": "05-global-sovereignty",
    "step": 1,
    "path": "audio/05-global-sovereignty/2.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 22098050,
    "text": "但你有一个不得不面对的事实: 在这场博弈里，个人的位置在哪？最底层。信息更少。迁移成本更高。很少参与规则制定。我们聊过的这些生产资料: prompt模板、判断标...",
    "localPath": "audio/05-global-sovereignty/2.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:84510bc47b1d44c7"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "05-global-sovereignty-3",
    "chapterId": "05-global-sovereignty",
    "step": 2,
    "path": "audio/05-global-sovereignty/3.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 13634649,
    "text": "Karp关心资本和企业，这是他站在那个位置的自然视角。但我们的立场不一样。我们关心的是每一个具体的人。尤其是那些还不知道自己正在交房租的人。",
    "localPath": "audio/05-global-sovereignty/3.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:a002c177636d8ca6"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "06-three-principles-1",
    "chapterId": "06-three-principles",
    "step": 0,
    "path": "audio/06-three-principles/1.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 34744354,
    "text": "好。现在把Karp给CEO开的处方，翻译成个人版本。三个原则。这三个原则和Karp的四个论点，是一一对应的。原则一: 你拥有你的判断标准。对应Karp的: 控制...",
    "localPath": "audio/06-three-principles/1.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:cda843857b402d81"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "06-three-principles-2",
    "chapterId": "06-three-principles",
    "step": 1,
    "path": "audio/06-three-principles/2.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 7113741,
    "text": "AI能复制你的输出，复制不了你的判断过程: 前提是你自己把它记下来了。",
    "localPath": "audio/06-three-principles/2.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:58da45a8cf4554fb"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "06-three-principles-3",
    "chapterId": "06-three-principles",
    "step": 2,
    "path": "audio/06-three-principles/3.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 16070431,
    "text": "原则二: 你的知识资产不在平台服务器上。对应Karp的四问。每一次你觉得这次和AI的对话还不错的时候，把那场对话存到本地。每一个好用的prompt，变成可复用的...",
    "localPath": "audio/06-three-principles/3.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:a64c968b3ffbd61b"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "06-three-principles-4",
    "chapterId": "06-three-principles",
    "step": 3,
    "path": "audio/06-three-principles/4.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 8309206,
    "text": "纯消耗和积累资产的区别: 前者结束后你少了一堆token，后者结束后你多了一个文件。",
    "localPath": "audio/06-three-principles/4.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:590f413d18628403"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "06-three-principles-5",
    "chapterId": "06-three-principles",
    "step": 4,
    "path": "audio/06-three-principles/5.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 24789524,
    "text": "原则三: 你可以随时切换工具而不损失能力。对应Karp的: 生产资料不被转移。你的判断标准、prompt模板、问题拆解方式、审美偏好: 这些才是你的生产资料。它...",
    "localPath": "audio/06-three-principles/5.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:20ae0aaec545049b"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "06-three-principles-6",
    "chapterId": "06-three-principles",
    "step": 5,
    "path": "audio/06-three-principles/6.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 17970884,
    "text": "这三个原则不是在让你立刻去买GPU跑本地模型。不是那个意思。一个更简单的起点: 从今天开始，每一次觉得这次对话还不错，存下来。不用整理。不用分类。先存。",
    "localPath": "audio/06-three-principles/6.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:9aa47dd5381c3786"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "06-three-principles-7",
    "chapterId": "06-three-principles",
    "step": 6,
    "path": "audio/06-three-principles/7.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 10923628,
    "text": "这个动作本身就是主权化的第一步。它意味着你开始意识到: 这次对话里，有我的痕迹。而这个我，值得被自己保留。",
    "localPath": "audio/06-three-principles/7.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:f17bb08e091274a2"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "07-ending-1",
    "chapterId": "07-ending",
    "step": 0,
    "path": "audio/07-ending/1.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 5031655,
    "text": "Karp在访谈最后说了一句话: The jig is up。骗局曝光了。",
    "localPath": "audio/07-ending/1.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:138fb50a1fbc8342"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "07-ending-2",
    "chapterId": "07-ending",
    "step": 1,
    "path": "audio/07-ending/2.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 30480091,
    "text": "我说不准他的骗局具体指什么。但他提出的四个问题: 谁拥有数据、数据存在哪、提示是否安全、信息是否传输给第三方: 这些问题，不只是企业CEO需要答案。你每次打开A...",
    "localPath": "audio/07-ending/2.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:94627e1b7934fe9c"
  },
  {
    "segmentId": "07-ending-3",
    "chapterId": "07-ending",
    "step": 2,
    "path": "audio/07-ending/3.aiff",
    "voice": "Tingting",
    "provider": "macos-say",
    "durationUs": 24199728,
    "text": "Karp那个卖药的人，把病历公开了。要不要给自己号个脉，是你的事。好，这就是今天的内容。在弹幕或评论区聊聊: 你目前用AI的方式，积累资产和纯消耗，哪种更多？这...",
    "localPath": "audio/07-ending/3.aiff",
    "hash": "sha256:97434269cc42f4e9"
  },
